                <h1>Who Makes Rivian: The Story Behind the Electric Vehicle Innovator</h1>
                <p>Rivian is an American electric vehicle manufacturer founded by RJ Scaringe in 2009. The company focuses on producing all-electric trucks and SUVs, with the R1T pickup and R1S SUV being its flagship models. Rivian's vision combines sustainability with innovation, aiming to redefine the future of transportation.</p>
